{"id": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie__a2-late-chunking__0002", "text": "We expect the food industry to grow by 1 percent in volume by 2025. Domestic demand is increasing and exports are also increasing this year. We expect stabilization before 2026. The unpredictability, especially in international supply chains, is increasing. In this video, sector economist Melanie Murk explains in 2 minutes what challenges the food sector faces and what you can do as an entrepreneur.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie__a2-late-chunking__0002", "source_slug": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie", "source_title": "Volume growth is back in the food industry", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/food/volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie.html", "source_date": "2025-08-14", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "sectorprognoses", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 2}}
