{"id": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie__a2-late-chunking__0005", "text": "## Security of supply and higher costs remain current", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie__a2-late-chunking__0005", "source_slug": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie", "source_title": "Volume growth is back in the food industry", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/food/volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie.html", "source_date": "2025-08-14", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "sectorprognoses", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 5}}
{"id": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie__a2-late-chunking__0006", "text": "The extreme price increases are over for the time being, although some product groups such as coffee and cocoa are still affected as a result of crop failures due to climate change.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie__a2-late-chunking__0006", "source_slug": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie", "source_title": "Volume growth is back in the food industry", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/food/volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie.html", "source_date": "2025-08-14", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "sectorprognoses", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 6}}
{"id": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie__a2-late-chunking__0007", "text": "In addition, wage costs have risen sharply in recent years. In combination with a labor shortage, this leads to more investments in automation and robotization.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie__a2-late-chunking__0007", "source_slug": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie", "source_title": "Volume growth is back in the food industry", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/food/volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie.html", "source_date": "2025-08-14", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "sectorprognoses", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 7}}
{"id": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "Also read the publication [International chains increase unpredictability in the food industry](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/food/internationale-ketens-vergroten-onvoorspelbaarheid-in-voedingsindustrie.html). In this publication we discuss the forecasts for 2025 and 2026, which are influenced by higher domestic and foreign demand on the one hand and higher labor costs, unpredictability of international supply chains and raw material prices on the other.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie", "source_title": "Volume growth is back in the food industry", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/food/volumegroei-is-terug-in-de-voedingsindustrie.html", "source_date": "2025-08-14", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "sectorprognoses", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
